import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import emailjs, { type EmailJSResponseStatus } from '@emailjs/browser'; @Component({ selector: 'app-correo', templateUrl: './correo.component.html', styleUrls: ['./correo.component.css'] }) export class CorreoComponent { public sendEmail(e: Event) { e.preventDefault(); emailjs .sendForm('service_o0dju72', 'template_fw98ehe', e.target as HTMLFormElement, { publicKey: '3fssA4Flpz0Pbiqhu', }) .then( () => { console.log('SUCCESS!'); }, (err) => { console.log('FAILED...', (err as EmailJSResponseStatus).text); }, ); } } Formulario de Contacto
